**WHERE:** _Batman/Superman: World’s Finest_ #37 is available to preorder now at participating comic book shops. For the shop nearest you, visit the Comic Shop Locator website, [https://www.comicshoplocator.com](https://www.comicshoplocator.com/).

 **WHEN:** _Batman/Superman: World’s Finest_ #37 is available at participating comic book shops and digital retailers on Wednesday, March 19, 2025. For more information on DC, follow @DCOfficial on social media (and @[dc.com](http://dc.com/) on Bluesky), or visit the official DC website at [https://www.dc.com](https://www.dc.com/).